                                        <h5 class="card-subtitle "><a class="belt-link" href="/en/Blogs/Articles/2023/06/11/middle-east-north-africa-vulnerable-to-rising-fiscal-risks ">Middle East, North Africa Vulnerable to Rising Fiscal Risks</a></h5>
                                        <time class="card-date mb-2 text-muted" datetime="6/11/2023 3:00:00 AM">June 11, 2023</time>
                                        <p class="card-text "><a href="/en/Blogs/Articles/2023/06/11/middle-east-north-africa-vulnerable-to-rising-fiscal-risks">Stronger risk management can reduce budgetary surprises and allow the region to plan better for development.</a></p>
